#. type: Title #
#: manual/Interoperability.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Interoperability with Other Network File Systems"
msgstr "他のネットワークファイルシステムとの相互運用性"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:6
msgid ""
"Netatalk and Samba can share the same volume and store Extended Attribute "
"metadata in a mutually compatible format, enabling access via AFP or SMB."
msgstr ""
"Netatalk と Samba は同じボリュームを共有し、拡張属性メタデータを相互互換のあ"
"る形式で保存できるため、AFP または SMB 経由でのアクセスが可能になる。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> ***WARNING:*** The **ea = samba** and **ea = sys** (Netatalk default)\n"
"> metadata formats are **not** compatible,\n"
"> and there is currently no automated way to convert between them.\n"
"> If you have an existing Netatalk volume using the default settings and want to add Samba sharing,\n"
"> the recommended migration path is to copy files from one volume to another using an AFP client.\n"
msgstr ""
"> 【警告】 **ea = samba** と **ea = sys** (Netatalk デフォルト) の\n"
"> メタデータ形式は互換性が**ない**。\n"
"> 現時点では、両形式の間で自動的に変換する方法はない。\n"
"> デフォルト設定を使用している既存の Netatalk ボリュームに Samba 共有を追加したい場合は、\n"
"> AFP クライアントを使用してファイルを別のボリュームにコピーすることが推奨の移行方法である。\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:18
msgid ""
"When sharing a volume with other processes (Samba, NFS, local applications), "
"keep *dircache validation freq* at **1** (the default)  so Netatalk detects "
"external changes on every access.  If Netatalk is the **only** process on "
"the volume, you can set *dircache validation freq* = 100 for maximum "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"Samba、NFS、ローカルアプリケーションなど他のプロセスとボリュームを共有する場"
"合は、Netatalk がアクセスのたびに外部の変更を検出できるよう、*dircache "
"validation freq* を **1** (デフォルト) のままにしておくこと。Netatalk がその"
"ボリュームの**唯一の**プロセスであれば、最大パフォーマンスのために *dircache "
"validation freq* = 100 に設定できる。"

#. type: Title ##
#: manual/Interoperability.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Netatalk configuration"
msgstr "Netatalk の設定"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:22
msgid ""
"Use *ea = samba* to store Extended Attributes in the Samba-compatible format."
msgstr "*ea = samba* を使用して、Samba 互換形式で拡張属性を保存する。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [Global]\n"
"        vol preset = my default values\n"
"        dircache validation freq = 1\n"
"        ea = samba\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [Homes]\n"
"        basedir regex = /home\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:33 manual/Interoperability.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [Test Volume]\n"
"        path = /export/test1\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:37
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [My Time Machine Volume]\n"
"        path = /export/timemachine\n"
"        time machine = yes\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: manual/Interoperability.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "Samba configuration"
msgstr "Samba の設定"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:43
msgid ""
"The Samba **catia**, **fruit**, and **streams_xattr** VFS modules provide "
"compatibility for Apple SMB clients and interoperability with Netatalk.  Use "
"**hide files** (not **veto files**) to hide Netatalk's invisible files from "
"Windows clients."
msgstr ""
"Samba の **catia**、**fruit**、**streams_xattr** VFS モジュールは、Apple SMB "
"クライアントとの互換性および Netatalk との相互運用性を提供する。**veto "
"files** ではなく **hide files** を使用して、Netatalk の不可視ファイルを "
"Windows クライアントから隠す。"

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:47
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [global]\n"
"        ea support = yes\n"
"        vfs objects = catia fruit streams_xattr\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:51
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"        fruit:encoding = native\n"
"        streams_xattr:prefix = user.\n"
"        streams_xattr:store_stream_type = no\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "        hide files = /.DS_Store/Network Trash Folder/TheFindByContentFolder/TheVolumeSettingsFolder/Temporary Items/.TemporaryItems/.VolumeIcon.icns/Icon?/.FBCIndex/.FBCLockFolder/\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:55
#, no-wrap
msgid "        read only = no\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "    [homes]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: manual/Interoperability.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    [My Time Machine Volume]\n"
"        path = /export/timemachine\n"
msgstr ""
